tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE user_profiles (
    user_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    full_name VARCHAR(100),
    email VARCHAR(100) UNIQUE,
    date_of_birth DATE,
    address VARCHAR(255),
    phone_number VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE user_profiles (
	user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	first_name VARCHAR(50),
	last_name VARCHAR(50),
	email VARCHAR(100),
	phone_number VARCHAR(15)
);

CREATE TABLE user_preferences (
	user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	music_preference VARCHAR(50),
	audio_book_preference VARCHAR(50),
	driving_preference VARCHAR(50),
	language_preference VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE UserProfiles (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_name VARCHAR(50),
    email VARCHAR(100),
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10)
);

CREATE TABLE UserPreferences (
    user_id INT,
    preference_name VARCHAR(50),
    preference_value VARCHAR(100),
    PRIMARY KEY (user_id, preference_name),
    FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES UserProfiles(user_id) ON DELETE CASCADE
);

CREATE TABLE VehiclePreferences (
    vehicle_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    playback_volume INT,
    temperature INT,
    ambient_lighting VARCHAR(20),
    FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES UserProfiles(user_id) ON DELETE CASCADE
);

CREATE TABLE UserProfile (
    user_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    first_name VARCHAR(50),
    last_name VARCHAR(50),
    email VARCHAR(100),
    phone_number VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE VehicleInfo (
    vehicle_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    make VARCHAR(50),
    model VARCHAR(50),
    year INT,
    color VARCHAR(20),
    license_plate VARCHAR(15)
);

CREATE TABLE UserVehicle (
    user_vehicle_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID,
    vehicle_id UUID,
    FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES UserProfile(user_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (vehicle_id) REFERENCES VehicleInfo(vehicle_id)
);
